[0.018, "o", "\u001b[0;1;32m●\u001b[0m php-fpm-legacy.service - The PHP FastCGI Process Manager\r\n     Loaded: loaded (\u001b]8;;file://advan/usr/lib/systemd/system/php-fpm-legacy.service\u001b\\/usr/lib/systemd/system/php-fpm-legacy.service\u001b]8;;\u001b\\; \u001b[0;1;32menabled\u001b[0m; preset: \u001b[0;1;33m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mdisabled\u001b[0m)\r\n     Active: \u001b[0;1;32mactive (running)\u001b[0m since Tue 2026-06-09 05:20:39 WIB; 4s ago\r\n Invocation: cf680b3732e94615bf278edff564ce88\r\n   Main PID: 3315 (php-fpm-legacy)\r\n     Status: \"\u001b[0;1;36mReady to handle connections\u001b[0m\"\r\n      Tasks: 3\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m (limit: 4331)\u001b[0m\r\n     Memory: 6.2M (peak: 6.5M)\r\n        CPU: 67ms\r\n     CGroup: /system.slice/php-fpm-legacy.service\r\n             ├─\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m3315 \"php-fpm: master process (/etc/php-legacy/php-fpm.conf)\"\u001b[0m\r\n             ├─\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m3316 \"php-fpm: pool www\"\u001b[0m\r\n             └─\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m3317 \"php-fpm: pool www\"\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nJun 09 05:20:39 advan systemd[1]: Starting The PHP FastCGI Process Manager...\r\nJun 09 05:20:39 advan php-fpm[3315]: \u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;31m\u001b[0;1;39m[NOTICE] fpm is running, pid 3315\u001b[0m\r\nJun 09 05:20:39 advan php-fpm[3315]: \u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;31m\u001b[0;1;39m[NOTICE] ready to handle connections\u001b[0m\r\nJun 09 05:20:39 advan php-fpm[3315]: \u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;31m\u001b[0;1;39m[NOTICE] systemd monitor interval set to 10000ms\u001b[0m\r\nJun 09 05:20:39 advan systemd[1]: Started The PHP FastCGI Process Manager.\r\n"]
